\n咁你咪出黎吠啦<br />\n定你老母車你個陣都係咁所以你以為全世界都應該係咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喂我驚蟲、怕血所以唔揸車，同我回唔回呢個post有咩關係呀？依家淨係車主先有資格評論新聞？你自己出黎吠我話我係公路炸彈咋喎，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我依家咪同你講我無揸車，唔係你擔憂範圍之內囉戇鳩</span></span></blockquote><br />\n無啦啦有飛蟑螂飛落你個身度丫 包你同條女差唔多咁炒車<br />\n<br />\n喂你唔撚識渣車就唔好沖出黎柒啦<br />\n紅色大字就你羸啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上面留嗰句野邊度唔客觀呀？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">根本司機就唔嚇得架啦</span><br />\n唔係邊得黎咁多人半夜撞鬼/見到影<br />\n以為自己就黎撞到人就即刻扭軚撞樹/撞壆死埋？<br />\n又唔見你屌鳩呢啲人？<br />\n我無考車唔代表我唔識道路規則、唔識點操作架車囉"},{"pid":"27d001fa7497b45289d53c1b3b0e4b39ba0a1bc5","tid":335141,"uid":121854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:18:35.000Z","msg":"如果係有隻大蜘蛛無啦啦跳左上隻手 我諗得連孟仔唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957b0e848090e381fd2a1249d7d2f065a9fd77e4","tid":335141,"uid":121854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:19:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係有隻大蜘蛛無啦啦跳左上隻手 我諗得連登仔唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8dcbfad8aaf95bf2efe2ea87de37c7421cbdc1f1","tid":335141,"uid":10079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"成個叉仔咁喎"},{"pid":"7135bb7faf09a21aa10d7f84b0ae182c1a787ca5","tid":335141,"uid":35706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:24:18.000Z","msg":"男人黎wo<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0574daef1841103e0903ed9e869d4d039fb157","tid":335141,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你試下係啲唔停得車既路度渣車，無啦啦有飛蟑螂飛落你個身度丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 包你同條女差唔多咁炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor